<p><strong>SCP-CN-1169 不纯粹虚构社交组织</strong></p>
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ninth-bb" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4370469); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4370469&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601039779" alt="Ninth BB" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4370469)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ninth-bb" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4370469); return false;">Ninth BB</a></span></p>
